{
  "stem": "18575.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I went over, there was a wooden-- wooden-- there was-- it was the street closed and there was a wooden fence.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That night, I just jumped the fence.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I went to the house of a person that I knew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My father knew him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was the-- the alteste of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "What they call that, the-- the-- the ghetto altester, the leader, so to say, that the Germans appointed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He knew my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He knew me well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I woke him up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Knock on the window and he came out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He heard about us being arrested.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But he didn't know what happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I told him what happened, you know, the execution.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He-- I was, by the way, I only had a shirt and pants.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I had no jacket.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "My finger were totally frozen, like wood, like pieces of wood.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so were my toes and my ears.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was third degree burn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "If you hit it, it was just like you would hit piece of metal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he gave me some old clothing and gave me a hat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because my head was shaved.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- they shear my hair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And pair of glasses, although I never wore glasses then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And put me into a synagogue in the village, in the town, that was used to shelter people the Germans have thrown out of-- of neighboring villages.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They all pushed them to Krzemieniec.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were hundreds of them laying on the floor there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was among them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was there a few days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by-- by the way, the alteste-- I don't remember his name-- but after he heard the story, he says, Adam, you gonna survive the war.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know where the heck he knew that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But, anyway.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I lay there for couple days.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
